notes: The year 2006 is a time for celebration for Nissan Motor Firm, Ltd. Why, you could ask? Let us just say that just lately, this auto maker has just reached a new milestone in its existence. Nissan has now produced its 100 millionth vehicle final June. Just envision the whole range of autos that this vehicle maker has been capable to produce and bring out to the streets and roads. So far, the company has been in a position to manufacture some 76,640,000 units of Nissan cars and vehicles in its house country which is Japan. The rest of the lot has been designed in its different manufacturing plants scattered all about the globe. The production of Nissan does not only quit at generating vehicles and autos. The business is also accountable for manufacturing the finest Nissan auto components produced just for the use of their vehicles. This Japanese auto maker has also produced sure that production of autos does not finish with its 100 millionth automobile. For at the finish of June, which is also the month wherein the 100 millionth Nissan car was completed, the organization was able to make a total of 100,140,000 units of Nissan vehicles. The Nissan Motor Business, Limited is actually a brand of autos which has been sent out to the auto industry beneath a various name years ahead of. Datsun was the brand that these automobiles held.
